-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A\u00eft\u00a0Ben\u00a0Haddou\u00a0day\u00a0trip\u00a0gives you an opportunity to discover one of the most beautiful\u00a0and\u00a0oldest Kasbahs in Morocco. the driver will pick you up from your accommodation in Marrakech then take the road to A\u00eft\u00a0Ben\u00a0Haddou by crossing the high Atlas Mountains Tizi n Tichka ( 2262 m ).<\/p><p>A\u00eft\u00a0Ben\u00a0Haddou is a fortified city, or palace (ksar), along with the former caravan route between the Sahara\u00a0and\u00a0Marrakech in present-day\u00a0Morocco. Most citizens living in the area now live in more modern dwellings in a nearby village. It has been a UNESCO World Heritage Site since 1987. You will have a visit of this Kasbah to explore the Berber architecture. Then you will have lunch, after lunch taking the road back to Marrakech.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-68a4c31 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"68a4c31\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Book Now<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-2da6da2 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"2da6da2\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-8a6e95d\" data-id=\"8a6e95d\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ab632ac ekit_wpForms